Description: GUI helper for Waydroid configuration and extensions
 Waydroid Helper is a graphical user interface application that provides
 a user-friendly way to configure Waydroid and install extensions,
 including Magisk, ARM translation, and various Google services alternatives.
 .
 Features include:
  * Configure Waydroid settings
  * Install Magisk
  * Install ARM translation (libhoudini/libndk)
  * Install Google services (OpenGapps/MindTheGapps/MicroG)
  * Install SmartDock 
